<node id="Spring 2026">
  <data key="d0">Spring 2026</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Spring 2026 refers to an academic semester during which a variety of CSCE courses are scheduled to be offered. This period serves as the academic semester for the listed courses.

Specifically, courses planned for Spring 2026 include CSCE 608, CSCE 611, CSCE 612, CSCE 624, and CSCE 633. Additionally, the Analysis of Algorithms course (CSCE 629), CSCE 638 Section 600, and CSCE 641 are also slated to be taught during this semester.

Further offerings for the Spring 2026 academic semester encompass CSCE 656, the Computational Optimization course (CSCE 669), CSCE 670 Section 600, CSCE 672, and CSCE 676.&lt;SEP&gt;Spring 2026 is the academic semester and year during which the CSCE 679 course is offered.&lt;SEP&gt;The academic semester when the CSCE 681 course is scheduled to take place.&lt;SEP&gt;The academic semester during which the CSCE 713 course is offered.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4787791f3cadc06a986e7b27db04ada7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d60e9b89876ff4f208f83d4690326716&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5da1285c39cd0b664efd61b2c39e1d9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c31aae19f8195c609e8290aa6aa9faf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e77bac3e3db3041b92245e5624c1506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf8027e07646b3347718ee94db7b859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c6bcb13e5ca1ef1edf824fccc07042&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1192343e60f6ed435822dac61ce0739&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7c81f6e4494e10258942389c914640a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-357e6bdf7fcde308683911146d776375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b810234bec8f8c12bc43ff0e5795f51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ce31af43e65fb24031c482d08c7273d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a9af8f71d37ea6626a8af485b77b7d6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1171d3689486ddcc85ff23150117d15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c66b4287d564818d44d58a6879b7417&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85da6717468da912a7312b2acddb5377&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-495327852159dc9e156c8c987052e067&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74abb1823920a1537264245d188ac80b</data>
