<node id="College Station">
  <data key="d0">College Station</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">College Station is identified as a geographical location, specifically a city, that serves as a venue for various academic activities. It is widely recognized as the primary location where numerous courses and their associated meetings are held, taught, or offered.

Specifically, College Station hosts a range of Computer Science and Engineering (CSCE) courses, including CSCE 608, CSCE 611, CSCE 612, CSCE 624, CSCE 633, CSCE 641, CSCE 656, CSCE 672, CSCE 676, and CSCE 679. Additionally, the Analysis of Algorithms course is conducted in College Station. The city consistently functions as the site for these and other general course offerings and meetings.&lt;SEP&gt;The geographical location where the CSCE 681 course is offered.&lt;SEP&gt;The city where the CSCE 713 course is held.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4787791f3cadc06a986e7b27db04ada7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d60e9b89876ff4f208f83d4690326716&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5da1285c39cd0b664efd61b2c39e1d9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c31aae19f8195c609e8290aa6aa9faf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e77bac3e3db3041b92245e5624c1506&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf8027e07646b3347718ee94db7b859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42c6bcb13e5ca1ef1edf824fccc07042&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1192343e60f6ed435822dac61ce0739&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7c81f6e4494e10258942389c914640a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-357e6bdf7fcde308683911146d776375&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b810234bec8f8c12bc43ff0e5795f51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4ce31af43e65fb24031c482d08c7273d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1171d3689486ddcc85ff23150117d15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c66b4287d564818d44d58a6879b7417&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85da6717468da912a7312b2acddb5377&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-495327852159dc9e156c8c987052e067&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74abb1823920a1537264245d188ac80b</data>
