<node id="Final Exam">
  <data key="d0">Final Exam</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The final exam for the course is scheduled for May 4, Monday, from 10:30am to 12:30pm and accounts for 30% of the final grade.&lt;SEP&gt;A comprehensive in-class exam worth 30% of the final grade, scheduled for Thursday, 4/30 from 3:00pm-4:00pm.&lt;SEP&gt;The Final Exam is a comprehensive assessment for the course, scheduled for May 1, Friday (8:00 am – 10:00 am), and contributes 35% to the final grade.`</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb1296e293d05dc37ed35c31463ee77a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfd68ceb87515331e129a9abd37822bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-809541d0b262ea6632eaa5f05655b59d</data>
