<node id="Assignments">
  <data key="d0">Assignments</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Tasks or pieces of work given to students that are subject to submission deadlines and policies.&lt;SEP&gt;A course component worth 25% of the grade, completed individually or collaboratively, but distinct from group projects.&lt;SEP&gt;Tasks or projects given to students in the course, for which generative AI tools can be used as an assistance, not a replacement for completion.&lt;SEP&gt;Assignments represent a category of graded work contributing to the final grade in the course.&lt;SEP&gt;Tasks given to students for which late days can be used, but not including the final project.&lt;SEP&gt;Course activities that involve programming and contribute to the final grade.</data>
