  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An absence from class or work that is deemed valid by university or course policy, making the student eligible for makeup work without penalty.&lt;SEP&gt;An absence that is recognized as valid, making makeup work exempt from late penalties and potentially leading to extensions.&lt;SEP&gt;An authorized reason for a student's absence, which exempts makeup work from the late work policy.&lt;SEP&gt;A valid reason for a student's absence, which makes makeup work exempt from the late work policy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e6c491839f19e2ead354056f60e29d9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01325762279bde457b25b8a2357fe587&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f6459a98ec2442f228c8ad996357aaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e61c7d052ddb26fad7475ce76968aeb</data>
