  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">CSCE 432 is a course designation where Pre-Class Engagement accounts for 10% of the grade.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific course for which the Literature Review is 0% of the grade and the Current Research Presentation is 10%.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-686108f24ad2964e2eb6746fc5d77479&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5894fe93e51bdc7af7bed3d548cd3ac</data>
